Vulois

Vuulois rubbed away his tears and smiled.

"Yeah, you're right. Battera's probably really upset. But in here we 
can't use our comms. I've still got a small communication system 
here. I hope it can get as far as the Cybertronian Fire. Let's try 
it."

Vulois walks over to the comm machine, and tries to send it to 
Battera.

"Battera...can you here me? It's Vulois. We made it! You can relax 
now. I'll take command back."

Vulois than sent a message to Afterburner.

"Afterburner...it's Vulois. Can you here me? The three of us have 
made it. We're alright. Is everything okay in the embassy?"
